title: Stacey's Dad
alt: I bet she gets you to mow the lawn, doesn't she?
transcript:
[A hairy man.]
Man: Look, I know you think that since I walked out she could use a guy like you. But trust me. That woman has got a lot going on, and you want none of it. 
Man: Get out while you still can.[Printed across the bottom of the panel.]
Stacey's dad.
